      <section class="detail-section">
        <h2>What's Next</h2>
        <p>Ad-Apt is evolving. The agency model taught me everything about what businesses actually need from marketing — and those lessons are being productized into <a href="/projects/onit">Onit</a>. The core insight: most businesses need sophisticated marketing but can't afford $10K/month agency retainers. Onit is the answer to that gap — AI-powered execution with the strategic depth of an agency. Ad-Apt continues to serve existing clients while the next chapter takes shape.</p>
